vote.title: Authorize (1) the first amendment to the lease with the United States Customs and Border Protection (“CBP”) at Dallas Love Field (the “Airport”) to extend the lease by two one-year terms with an additional one-year renewal option to support its operations at the Airport; and (2) a reimbursement in an estimated amount of $5,000.00, annually for utilities servicing the CBP leasehold - Estimated amount of $15,000.00 - Financing: Aviation Fund (see Fiscal Information)
